> I have the same problem on arm64:
`FATA[0000] Error loading trust policy: open /etc/containers/policy.json: no such file or directory`

> Refer to the [official](https://github.com/containers/skopeo/blob/main/default-policy.json) solution: 
```shell
$ mkdir -p /etc/containers
$ tee > /etc/containers/policy.json <<-EOF
{
    "default": [
        {
            "type": "insecureAcceptAnything"
        }
    ],
    "transports":
        {
            "docker-daemon":
                {
                    "": [{"type":"insecureAcceptAnything"}]
                }
        }
}
EOF
